00020 # /* BOOST_PP_TUPLE_TO_LIST */

00022 # if ~BOOST_PP_CONFIG_FLAGS() & BOOST_PP_CONFIG_MWCC()
00023 #    define BOOST_PP_TUPLE_TO_LIST(size, tuple) BOOST_PP_TUPLE_TO_LIST_I(size, tuple)
00024 #    if ~BOOST_PP_CONFIG_FLAGS() & BOOST_PP_CONFIG_MSVC()
00025 #        define BOOST_PP_TUPLE_TO_LIST_I(s, t) BOOST_PP_TUPLE_TO_LIST_ ## s t
00026 #    else
00027 #        define BOOST_PP_TUPLE_TO_LIST_I(s, t) BOOST_PP_TUPLE_TO_LIST_II(BOOST_PP_TUPLE_TO_LIST_ ## s t)
00028 #        define BOOST_PP_TUPLE_TO_LIST_II(res) res
00029 #    endif
00030 # else
00031 #    define BOOST_PP_TUPLE_TO_LIST(size, tuple) BOOST_PP_TUPLE_TO_LIST_OO((size, tuple))
00032 #    define BOOST_PP_TUPLE_TO_LIST_OO(par) BOOST_PP_TUPLE_TO_LIST_I ## par
00033 #    define BOOST_PP_TUPLE_TO_LIST_I(s, t) BOOST_PP_TUPLE_TO_LIST_ ## s ## t
00034 # endif
